    <item>
      <title>叙利亚暴力事件激增，前阿萨德政权部队造成 14 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/ex-assad-regime-forces-kill-14-as-syria-sees-upsurge-in-violence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据叙利亚看守政府称，效忠前叙利亚总统巴沙尔·阿萨德的部队杀死了 14 名警察，造成 10 人受伤。自本月初独裁者倒台以来，该国经历了最严重的暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-26/ex-assad-regime-forces-kill-14-as-syria-sees-upsurge-in-violence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Dec 2024 08:39:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
